high_descs: Turn left and walk into the bedroom and reach the sidetable in front of the bed.
Pick up the newspaper from the top of the shelf.
Move left to exit the room and walk straight to the floor lamp.
Switch on the floorlamp to examine the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper under the floorlamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the sidetable.
Pick the newspaper from the table.
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper by the floorlamp.

high_descs: Go straight turn right towards the sidetable.
Turn right and then turn left towards the newspaper.
And then take the newspaper from the table and then turn right and turn left towards the floorlamp.
Show the newspaper by the light of a floorlamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a floorlamp.
